test_even_range:
assert [32, 34] == [66, 68, 70, 72]
  At index 0 diff: 32 != 66
  Right contains 2 more items, first extra item: 70
  Full diff:
  - [66, 68, 70, 72]
  + [32, 34]
test_large_range:
assert [32, 33, 34] == [33, 34, 35, 36]
  At index 0 diff: 32 != 33
  Right contains one more item: 36
  Full diff:
  - [33, 34, 35, 36]
  + [32, 33, 34]
